{"lemma":"دُهْنُ","slug":"دُهْنُ","root":"د.ه.ن","root_slug":"د-ه-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ه-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"دُهْن","root":"دهن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n13304","n13305","n13306","n13307"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%87%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hit, to strike"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to smear, to spread"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to smear, to spread; to paint, to pigment"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deceive, to trick, to fool, to befool"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deceive, to trick, to fool, to befool; to flatter, to humor, to appease"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"synonym of دَهَنَ (dahana)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of دَهَنَ (dahana) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"],"examples":[{"text":"شُوكُولَاتَةٌ قَابِلَةٌ لِلدَّهْنِ","english":"chocolate spread"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"smeared substance, grease, fat"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"oily, greasy"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root د ه ن (d h n). Semantically like German streichen."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13304","headword_ar":"دَهْنٌ","root":"dhn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonN","text_ar":"دُهْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N dahonN","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ دَهْنٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Bad and scanty"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of subsistence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (JK.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13305","headword_ar":"دُهْنٌ","root":"dhn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Oil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Msb, KL,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grease of any kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhon","text_ar":"دُهْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sesame &c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one anoints,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greases,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moistens,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mustache,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hair &c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the head &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) it is well known: (S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonapN","text_ar":"دُهْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [or this latter, being the n. un., signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of oil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as the former does when it is prefixed to another noun:] you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonu AlbaAni","text_ar":"دُهْنُ البَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and Mgh and Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bwn","text_ar":"بون"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonapu baAnK","text_ar":"دُهْنَةُ بَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in the present art. from a poet) [both meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oil of ben"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: the pl. (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonN","text_ar":"دُهْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, Msb, and Bd in lv. 37) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dihaAnN","text_ar":"دِهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, and Bd ubi suprà) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adohaAnN","text_ar":"اَدْهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [the latter a pl. of pauc.; both pls. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kinds of oil &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~ihaAnu","text_ar":"الدِّهَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that with which one anoints;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd ubi suprà) or it has this signification also: (TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahanotuhu biAld~ihaAni","text_ar":"دَهَنْتُهُ بِالدِّهَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I anointed him with oils"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with ointment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, in which this is mentioned as an ex. of the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhonN","text_ar":"دُهْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and hence the prov."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAld~ihaAni EalaY Alwabari","text_ar":"كَالدِّهَانِ عَلَى الوَبَرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Like"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ointment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that with which one anoints"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon fur,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dihaAnN","text_ar":"دِهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.] ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weak rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain such as moistens the surface of the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahonN","text_ar":"دَهْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dihaAnN","text_ar":"دِهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, S, K.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vertigo"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwaAr","text_ar":"دُوَار"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that affects the camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","Msb","KL","Mgh","K","S","TA","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n13306","headword_ar":"دِهْنٌ","root":"dhn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of tree with which beasts of prey are killed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and by means of which they are taken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a noxious tree, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"difolaY","text_ar":"دِفْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as is large, of trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n13307","headword_ar":"دَهِنٌ","root":"dhn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Oily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greasy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) You say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN mudohaAn~N","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ مُدْهَانٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahinu Al$~aEari","text_ar":"دَهِنُ الشَّعَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man having oily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greasy, hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dahiynN","text_ar":"دَهِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}